Package: deckhand2
Title: Create slide decks and grid layout paginated HTML reports
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matt", "Kerlogue", , "matt.kerlogue@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An extension to the pagedown package that uses the CSS grid layout
    module to provide extensive layout control of page based Rmarkdown reports. 
